        <Parent_String>floor coverings [300186091], coverings and hangings for surface elements [300236483], coverings and hangings by location or context [300197364], coverings and hangings by specific type [300185832], coverings and hangings [300205012], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
